Title: mk_oracle: Fixed reference to all found SIDs in custom sqls
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1605801600
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i2

In the help text is the assignment of <i>SQLS_SIDS="\$SIDS"</i> an example
to assign a custom sql to all found instances. This has not been working,
since the config loaded before the script looked for running instances. The
example configuration of the help text will finally work with this fix.
